                            <comment id="100397" author="adilger" created="Tue, 2 Dec 2014 10:33:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I unlinked several files from their parent directory using debugfs on a snapshot of my MDT.  The files had size=0 and only standard Lustre xattrs such as &lt;tt&gt;lov&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;lma&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;link&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Running &lt;tt&gt;e2fsck -f&lt;/tt&gt; on the modified filesystem resulted in the files being linked into lost+found.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
